title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 69-5.7 - Technical assistance
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 69-5.7 - Technical assistance

State Regulations

The department of Health shall provide technical assistance to approved rape crisis programs to implement training programs in accordance with the minimum standards set forth in this Subpart. Notes
